Steetz
</taxonomicName>
, but 
<taxonomicName id="03BE4D1FFF91FFCEFC36DD4E26306C48" box="[924,1036,598,624]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Lagenophora" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="44" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sundana">
<emphasis id="F6CAEA8EFF91FFCEFC36DD4E26306C48" box="[924,1036,598,624]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="44">L. sundana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
could possibly be raised from synonymy in the future (Wang &amp; Bean, unpubl. data).
</paragraph>
